issue.title: [CF 1010] BonusStamina not picking up warlock buff "blood pact"
issue.body:
The TellMeWhen v7.2.0 r7 buff type "BonusStamina" isn't recognising Blood Pact (warlock passive) as a stamina buff.


> Posted by CurseForge user Tenzian | Imported from CurseForge issue #1010 | Raw

comments.body:
